race.description: Stawell Trackside Bar & Bistro 3YO Maiden Plate
race.comment: SWEATBAND (9) spiked his figures when beaten a whisker at Nhill. Has been kept on the fresh side and will hit the line hard. RED RABBIT (8) races forward and can build on the distant placing at Colac. Keeps the 1.5kg claim and she will get every chance from an inside barrier. PRESTIGE ZERPRISE (11) hasn't been having the best of it at the provincials and finally draws an inside barrier. He's likely to go a lot better in country grade. THEYCALLMETHUNDER (4) also presents fourth up and is knocking on the door. Has the winkers on for the first time and further improvement can see him in the finish.
